title: 8' Picnic Table, ADA Compliant, Expanded Metal, Blue Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow  ✓ Blue thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading, & heat accumulation  ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (8) bag hooks    DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:   Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring ADA-compliant seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.     BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:   High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and a 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.     COMFORTABLE SEATING:   This 8' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while two bench seats measure 72" long x 11-1/2" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. Beveled edges and rounded corners ensure a safe, comfortable experience. It features 24" of clearance at each end to allow wheelchair users easy access, while the bench height measures 16-1/2" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.     RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:  Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.    INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:   Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.     Limited 7-Year Warranty

INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:   Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. description: ✓ 30.4 cu. ft. capacity & supports up to 3000 lbs   ✓ Reinforced steel wire with powder coat finish   ✓ Stackable when open & folds flat to save space     Store & transport bulk parts, inventory, materials, and more with the 30.4 cu. ft. capacity Global Industrial Folding Wire Container. title: 6' Rectangular Picnic Table, Perforated Metal, Blue Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight perforated metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Blue thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (6) bag hooks      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including hospitals, healthcare facilities, office buildings, and restaurants. BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop. RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded mounting tabs on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty perforated metal mesh benches & tabletop promotes airflow, limits snow & dust accumulation and standing water. The perforations punched into the metal are precisely placed to avoid the edges and assembly points, providing additional strength with a clean & elevated look versus expanded metal. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 46" Square Picnic Table, Expanded Metal, Gray Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Gray thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (28) acorn safety caps & (4) bag hooks      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.       BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 300-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.       COMFORTABLE SEATING:    This 46" square tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the four bench seats measure 38" long x 12" wide, allowing 2 average adults or kids to easily fit on each bench. Beveled edges and rounded corners ensure a safe & comfortable experience. Bench height measures 16-1/2" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.       RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.      INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow  ✓ Green thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading, & heat accumulation  ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (6) bag hooks    DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:   Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.     BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:   High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and a 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.     COMFORTABLE SEATING:   This 6' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the two bench seats measure 72" long x 12" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. Beveled edges and rounded corners ensure a safe & comfortable experience. Bench height measures 17" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.     RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:  Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.    INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:   Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.     Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 8' Picnic Table, ADA Compliant, Black, Expanded Metal, Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow  ✓ Black thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading, & heat accumulation  ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (8) bag hooks    DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:   Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring ADA-compliant seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.     BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:   High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and a 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.     COMFORTABLE SEATING:   This 8' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while two bench seats measure 72" long x 11-1/2" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. Beveled edges and rounded corners ensure a safe, comfortable experience. It features 24" of clearance at each end to allow wheelchair users easy access, while the bench height measures 16-1/2" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.     RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:  Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.    INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:   Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.     Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 8' Rectangular Picnic Table, Perforated Metal, Black Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight perforated metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Black thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (8) bag hooks      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including hospitals, healthcare facilities, office buildings, and restaurants. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.       BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.       COMFORTABLE SEATING:    This 8' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the two bench seats measure 96" long x 12" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. The smooth surface, beveled edges, and rounded corners ensure a safe & comfortable experience. Bench height measures 17" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.       RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded mounting tabs on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The punched hole pattern of the perforated metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.      INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty perforated metal mesh benches & tabletop promotes airflow, limits snow & dust accumulation and standing water. The perforations punched into the metal are precisely placed to avoid the edges and assembly points, providing additional strength with a clean & elevated look versus expanded metal. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

description: ✓ Strong, lightweight perforated metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Green thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware and (28) acorn safety caps      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including hospitals, healthcare facilities, office buildings, and restaurants. title: 6' Rectangular Picnic Table, Perforated Metal, Green Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight perforated metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Green thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (6) bag hooks      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including hospitals, healthcare facilities, office buildings, and restaurants. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.       BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.       COMFORTABLE SEATING:    This 6' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the two bench seats measure 72" long x 12" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. The smooth surface, beveled edges, and rounded corners ensure a safe & comfortable experience. Bench height measures 17" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.       RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded mounting tabs on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The punched hole pattern of the perforated metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.      INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty perforated metal mesh benches & tabletop promotes airflow, limits snow & dust accumulation and standing water. The perforations punched into the metal are precisely placed to avoid the edges and assembly points, providing additional strength with a clean & elevated look versus expanded metal. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 8' Picnic Table, ADA Compliant, Expanded Metal, Red Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow  ✓ Red thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading, & heat accumulation  ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (8) bag hooks    DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:   Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring ADA-compliant seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.     BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:   High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and a 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.     COMFORTABLE SEATING:   This 8' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while two bench seats measure 72" long x 11-1/2" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. Beveled edges and rounded corners ensure a safe, comfortable experience. It features 24" of clearance at each end to allow wheelchair users easy access, while the bench height measures 16-1/2" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.     RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:  Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.    INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:   Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.     Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 46" Round Picnic Table, Expanded Metal, Red Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Red thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware and (28) acorn safety caps      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring seating or dining options. BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 300-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop. RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 8' Rectangular Picnic Table, Expanded Metal, Blue Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow  ✓ Blue thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading, & heat accumulation  ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (16) acorn safety caps, & (8) bag hooks    DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:   Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.     BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:   High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 900-pound capacity per bench and a 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.     COMFORTABLE SEATING:   This 8' rectangular tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the two bench seats measure 96" long x 12" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. Beveled edges and rounded corners ensure a safe & comfortable experience. Bench height measures 17" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.     RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:  Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.    INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:   Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.     Limited 7-Year Warranty
product highlight: 1000-pound weight capacity,Thermoplastic coating on seats and tabletop stays cool in full sun,"Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes air flow"
product type: Outdoor Furniture > Outdoor Tables > Picnic Tables > Metal Picnic Tables > Furniture & Decor

title: 46" Square Picnic Table, Perforated Metal, Black Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight perforated metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Black thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware, (28) acorn safety caps, & (4) bag hooks      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including hospitals, healthcare facilities, office buildings, and restaurants. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.       BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 300-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.       COMFORTABLE SEATING:    This 46" square tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the four bench seats measure 38" long x 12" wide, allowing multiple adults to easily fit on each bench. The smooth surface, beveled edges, and rounded corners ensure a safe & comfortable experience. Bench height measures 16-1/2" from the ground to make it easy to sit down & stand up. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.       RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded mounting tabs on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The punched hole pattern of the perforated metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.      INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty perforated metal mesh benches & tabletop promotes airflow, limits snow & dust accumulation and standing water. The perforations punched into the metal are precisely placed to avoid the edges and assembly points, providing additional strength with a clean & elevated look versus expanded metal. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

title: 46" Round Picnic Table, Expanded Metal, Gray Global Industrial
description: ✓ Strong, lightweight expanded metal mesh promotes airflow    ✓ Gray thermoplastic coating resists corrosion, fading & heat accumulation   ✓ Includes stainless steel hardware and (28) acorn safety caps      DESIGNED FOR OUTDOORS:    Ideal for any outdoor setting, including schools, camps, parks, corporate or hospital break areas, and any outdoor environment requiring seating or dining options. Smooth, glossy thermoplastic exterior coating on the tabletop & benches is UV-resistant to protect from fading, is engineered to withstand summer heat & winter cold, and is thermal-stable to stay comfortable even in direct summer sun.       BUILT TO CARRY THE LOAD:    High weight capacities for the tabletop & benches ensure a safe & comfortable experience with a 300-pound capacity per bench and 1000-pound weight capacity for the tabletop.       COMFORTABLE SEATING:    This 46" round tabletop can hold all the food & beverages users bring, while the four bench seats measure 38" long x 12" wide, allowing 2 average adults or kids to easily fit on each bench. A center hole accepts umbrella poles up to 1-1/2" in diameter.       RESISTANCE TO THEFT & VANDALISM:   Welded brackets on the frame allow the table to be permanently anchored to concrete, asphalt, and other surfaces to deter theft. The open diamond pattern of the expanded metal makes an unappealing surface for graffiti and paint does not adhere well to the thermoplastic coating, making it easy to clean.      INDUSTRIAL STRENGTH:    Heavy-duty expanded metal mesh seats & tabletop promotes airflow, prevents snow & dust accumulation, and limits standing water. Heavy-gauge galvanized tubular steel frame is finished in a corrosion-resistant black powder coat. Stainless steel hardware won't rust or corrode over time and comes with plastic protective acorn nuts that prevent injuries from rubbing against exposed bolt ends.       Limited 7-Year Warranty

description: ✓ Top drop door for deposits without accessing safe  ✓ Anti-fish baffles prevent theft through the deposit door  ✓ All-steel with 1/2" door, 1" locking bolts, & dead bar     The 0.8 cu. ft. Global Industrial Front-Loading B-Rate Depository Safe offers a convenient way to collect and protect deposited money and valuables from theft and robbery. The drop door connects to the front-loading door to allow deposits without accessing the safe. It is ideal for commercial use, like retail, gas stations & convenience stores, where cash deposits from registers are frequent. This model features an electronic digital lock that allows for multiple combinations with a lockout mode if codes are entered incorrectly, with keyed backup entry in the event of a battery failure. The B-rate designation sets minimum construction and locking requirements and indicates that it has been designed to withstand entry attempts by a professional burglar using common tools for up to 30 minutes. B-rate safes are typically used in residential or small business applications where higher security measures are not needed. Limited 1-Year Warranty. description: ✓ Built to contain two 55-gallon drum   ✓ All-welded steel with high-visibility yellow finish  ✓ Drum rollers & 350 lb capacity storage shelf    Specifically designed to safely store two 55-gallon drums of flammable liquids and smaller containers, the manual-close Global Industrial 110 Gallon Drum Storage Safety Cabinet features rollers that keep the drums elevated off the cabinet's sump, while making it easier to load and unload drums. Integrated 2" flame vents help remove flammable or caustic vapors from the interior which reduces the chance of ignition. The cabinet is made with reinforced double-walled all-welded steel with 1-1/2" of air space between walls with a high-visibility yellow powder coat finish that is scratch-resistant and protects the steel from corrosion. The air space provides heat resistance and helps to maintain a lower internal temperature in the event of a fire for NFPA 251-compliance. Meets NFPA Code 30, OSHA requirements, UFC and EPA compliant.     Additional safety features: Multilingual external warning sign Internal retention chain holds drums in place Grounding attachment points Entry latch also accepts an user-supplied padlock 2" raised, leak-proof door sill    NOTE: Some state and municipalities may require self-closing doors on flammable safety cabinets. This cabinet has manual closing doors, please review your local ordinances prior to purchasing to ensure compliance.

title: Depository Safe, 20"W x 20"D x 30"H, 2 Doors, Digital Locks, Global Industrial
description: ✓ Top drop door for deposits without accessing safe  ✓ Anti-fish baffles prevent theft through the deposit door  ✓ All-steel with 1/2" door, 1" locking bolts, & dead bar     The 3.6 cu. ft. Global Industrial Front-Loading B-Rate Depository Safe offers a convenient way to collect and protect deposited money and valuables from theft and robbery. The drop door connects to the top front-loading door to allow deposits without accessing the safe, with a lower, unconnected compartment serving as a separate, isolated safe to restrict access even further. It is ideal for commercial use, like retail, gas stations & convenience stores, where cash deposits from registers are frequent. This model features two electronic digital locks that allows for multiple combinations with a lockout mode if codes are entered incorrectly, with keyed backup entry in the event of a battery failure. Each lock is keyed different for maximum protection. The all-steel body is protected with a black powder coat finish that is scratch- & corrosion-resistant. Additional security features include a 1/2" thick door, 1" locking bolts, and a heavy-duty dead bar that provides maximum strength and durability to withstand forced entry attempts. The B-rate designation sets minimum construction and locking requirements and indicates that it has been designed to withstand entry attempts by a professional burglar using common tools for up to 30 minutes. B-rate safes are typically used in residential or small business applications where higher security measures are not needed. Limited 1-Year Warranty.    Heavy-duty dead bar prevents door removal during a forced entry attempt  Anti-fish baffle prevents theft through the deposit door Two 9V battery-operated electronic locks with a spring-loaded relocking devices Backup keyed entry with a sets of keys for each lock Automatic lockout mode If combinations are entered incorrectly  Four pre-drilled anchor holes to secure the safe to the floor Batteries & mounting hardware included No assembly required
